data.question: How long do I have to pick up my order?
What do I need to bring to pick up my order?
When will my Ship-to-Store order be ready for pickup?
data.shortAnswer:
30 days, 1 question asked: How can we do better?

  • For any returns within the US and Canada, head over to our Returns Portal and we'll email you a pre-paid return label.
  • Feel free to wear the shoes outside to ensure it works with your every day.
  • Our masks are not eligible for returns or exchanges.
  • Custom made shoes and limited edition shoes are available for one exchange only.
  • We don't offer free returns for international orders yet and the customer must bear the cost for international shipping and returns.
  • For any acceptable international return, mention your order number on the package along with your name, please ship it to
